49:18.722 --> 49:20.623
- You saw what was
left of that bird.

49:20.624 --> 49:23.159
- What I saw was
the rotten remains

49:23.160 --> 49:25.761
of an escaped farm animal.

49:25.762 --> 49:29.031
Nothing more.

49:29.032 --> 49:31.734
- I'm telling you the truth.

49:31.735 --> 49:34.870
- See it through my eyes.

49:34.871 --> 49:39.943
I find you in the stable, alone,

49:41.044 --> 49:44.347
