your camera smashed,

49:44.348 --> 49:47.917
an empty glass of
bourbon on the porch.

49:47.918 --> 49:51.854
Can you at least
appreciate my perspective?

49:51.855 --> 49:54.724
- I understand how it must look.

49:54.725 --> 49:58.695
- What's really troubling
you, Mr. Dawles?

49:59.830 --> 50:02.365
It's in your eyes.

50:02.366 --> 50:05.634
Something deeper.

50:05.635 --> 50:08.671
Something personal.

50:08.672 --> 50:11.907
- I'm just trying to do
my job and that's it.

50:11.908 --> 50:15.745
- You are here to
perform a service, Henry.

50:15.746 --> 50:19.982
One that means a
great deal to me.

50:19.983 --> 50:23.353
Can I count on you?

50:24.955 --> 50:26.922
- Yeah.

50:26.923 --> 50:28.424
- Good.

50:28.425 --> 50:31.861
I had faith you'd
muster the will.

50:31.862 --> 50:33.896
Besides,

50:33.897 --> 50:37.734
I am growing quite
fond of your company.

50:38.568 --> 50:40.536
Get a good night's rest.

50:40.537 --> 50:43.640
I'll see you in the morning.

